  "texts": [
    "Djaidja et al. (2024) used MLP to employ FL to 5G and beyond networks, addressing the non-IID nature of the network.",
    "Advanced aggregation algorithms such as FedAvg, FedProx, FedPer, and SCAFFOLD were used to build a global model that detects anomalies like Neptune (DoS).",
    "However, the paper highlights challenges in handling non-IID data, with models like FedAvg struggling with weight divergence.",
    "SCAFFOLD shows better convergence, though none of the FL models match the accuracy of centralized models.",
    "Finally, Campos et al. (2024) proposed a model for securing intelligent transportation systems (ITS)."
